## {{#if (eq project.language "pt-BR")}}Validacao Obrigatoria{{else}}Mandatory Validation{{/if}}

{{#if (eq project.language "pt-BR")}}
Apos QUALQUER mudanca de schema, executar:
1. `make test-{{module.name}}` — Migrations up/down funcionam
2. Verificar contratos com modulos dependentes (backend)
3. Confirmar que migrations sao reversiveis
{{else}}
After ANY schema change, run:
1. `make test-{{module.name}}` — Migrations up/down work
2. Verify contracts with dependent modules (backend)
3. Confirm migrations are reversible
{{/if}}

